title: Favorite Childhood Songs + Riddle Me This + Easy Artist Nicknames
itunes:title: Favorite Childhood Songs + Riddle Me This + Easy Artist Nicknames
description:
Bobby and the crew share their favorite childhood songs. We play another round of "Riddle Me This" where show members have to try and guess the answer to various easy kids riddles. Plus, Bobby reads off artist's nicknames and everyone has to try and guess who he's talking about!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
